- Use `useQuery` and `useMutation` hooks for data fetching and state management.
- Implement query invalidation to keep data fresh and up-to-date.
- Utilize `React Query Devtools` for debugging and monitoring query states.
- Set up global query configurations for consistent behavior across your app.